            <title>[GROOVY-596] StackOverflowError when instanciate BeanInfo</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-596</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following script cause a StackOverflowError&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;class A extends java.beans.SimpleBeanInfo&lt;br/&gt;
{&lt;br/&gt;
}&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;a=new A()&lt;/p&gt;</description>
